{"tid":683810,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野鳥大鬧星光行 搞到警員索晒氣","createTime":"2018-05-30T04:12:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-30T04:56:23.000Z","uid":41404,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"47ef29762ef36ef4f79c3719246b377113b5e35d","tid":683810,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180530/large/1527652507_5700.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180530%2Flarge%2F1527652507_5700.jpg&h=d7b76413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野鳥走進警車車底(詹家志攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180530/large/1527652508_c551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180530%2Flarge%2F1527652508_c551.jpg&h=e20433ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野鳥飛到巴士站(詹家志攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180530/large/1527652510_3654.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180530%2Flarge%2F1527652510_3654.jpg&h=fe6169f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警員用紙皮箱生擒野鳥(詹家志攝)<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180530/large/1527652511_ba38.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180530%2Flarge%2F1527652511_ba38.jpg&h=e5ba4360&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n野鳥正等候漁護署人員到場撿走處理。(詹家志攝)<br />\n<br />\n早上11時，一頭懷疑受傷、貌似白鴿的野鳥，降臨尖沙嘴梳士巴利道3號星光行對開行人路，引起大批途人注目，野鳥胸口的羽毛鼓起，在人潮中狀甚威武。警員接報到場嘗試將野鳥生擒，但野鳥雖然不能高飛，但亦飛出巴士總站閃避，又飛進警車車底，一時間令警員手忙腳亂。不過，野鳥最後被警員用紙皮箱生擒，等候漁護署人員到場撿走處理。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180530/58254995\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180530%2F58254995&d=bJKBWPzbAlOPooFAOkuCoBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=8683166f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180530%2F58254995&h=2d18f672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180530/58254995</a>"},{"pid":"69d58b0985ef368147ca201b5e3c3047075f2a21","tid":683810,"uid":44333,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"紙皮都得？"},{"pid":"1b4c447d0943e894be548810e3383ba0697ebc26","tid":683810,"uid":63909,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:15:25.000Z","msg":"嗱"},{"pid":"1bbde168c8dd91cf2724332b1a39d29e36814951","tid":683810,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c84de60e05c55906c4ce9d858e0994eb27edb0b","tid":683810,"uid":55533,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:17:12.000Z","msg":"野雀撚狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e7c94532c03949953b5feb6e09cef34eba474c4","tid":683810,"uid":32399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:17:21.000Z","msg":"固姑故？！？！？！"},{"pid":"07796bf8e3d52323f157e45cbf83217112647dcb","tid":683810,"uid":171718,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"69d58b0985ef368147ca201b5e3c3047075f2a21","tid":683810,"uid":44333,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"紙皮都得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:17:45.000Z","msg":"香港警察呢就好撚蠢嘅"},{"pid":"180940fc0bb5673ab7b054b268da8fcdc33ef9bf","tid":683810,"uid":3818,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T04:18:46.000Z","msg":"紙皮都得 咁condom都得啦"},{"pid":"0b4a403a92d472a03da24ea50a0837731cfbc012","tid":683810,"uid":93784,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score"